# Normalize line endings project-wide so a contributor's local core.autocrlf
# setting can't silently reintroduce CRLF into files Linux CI/runtime must
# read as LF (shell scripts especially — a CRLF shebang line fails outright
# on Linux). See implementation/tracking/STATUS.md E0-S3 close-out notes for
# the concrete bug this fixed (gradlew committed non-executable + this guard
# added alongside it).
* text=auto eol=lf

*.bat text eol=crlf
gradlew text eol=lf
gradlew.bat text eol=crlf

*.jar binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
